      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-tbl-rsm-inx    >    w-det-tbl-rsm-ctr
                     go to exe-cph-lv0-rsm-500.
           if        w-det-tbl-rsm-inx    >    w-det-tbl-rsm-max
                     go to exe-cph-lv0-rsm-500.
